Goal: scaffold a new wallet adapter.

Inputs:
- provider: <string> (e.g. 'ledger')
- npmPackage: <string> (e.g. '@ledgerhq/hw-transport-webusb')

Steps:
1. Under packages/wallet-kit/adapters/<provider>/ create index.ts implementing WalletAdapter interface.
2. Add Jest unit tests with full Jest mocks for the provider SDK.
3. Ensure no coverage drop; adhere to rules.md section 2a.